{"tid":479464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藏旗在德國足球場飄揚 中國隊跳腳：今年不踢了","createTime":"2017-11-25T06:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T10:59:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"767fb597387e2d17605b45e2a615e454ca09f911","tid":479464,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnq3H6S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnq3H6S.jpg&h=4e89b60c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國U20足球國家隊赴德國訓練，原定與德國西南地區聯賽多支隊伍進行友誼賽，以強化2020東京奧運戰力。但在與美茵茲隊（TSV Schott Mainz）踢球時，場邊有觀眾在揮舞西藏「雪山獅子旗」，讓中國球員離場抗議。如今中國足協更決定，今年剩下的3場友誼賽全都不踢了，延遲到明年進行。<br />\n<br />\n中國足協發出新聞稿，表示「中國U20選拔隊將推遲在德系列友誼賽」，文中強調中國U20選拔隊與德國西南地區聯賽各隊的友誼對抗，其初衷是為了加強兩國的互相了解，並增進中國足球發展，孰料卻受到非體育因素的介入，干擾了比賽的進行。<br />\n<br />\n中國足協指出，這些非體育的行為，並不符合中德發展友好關係的原則，也牴觸了國際足聯的規定，因此決定把2017年和德國西南地區聯賽各隊的3場友誼賽，全部都改到2018年再踢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2264300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2264300&d=N8XfqDuzeZiIqZa3Yt1pizPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=71e41077\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2264300&h=10cc45dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2264300</a>"},{"pid":"5abd7dda05309aaa14c35030394048167e685672","tid":479464,"uid":41116,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"想支那人唔黎？揮藏旗"},{"pid":"eb609e2ce01cdead3c59c48dfa08b7e34150fe5b","tid":479464,"uid":81113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"怕輸就怕輸啦大陸喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536e61b2d32f5dadaae5efac7c8116c2bf9b7faa","tid":479464,"uid":41292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c